{"tid":1017239,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國民主黨迎來第九位總統候選人角逐者","createTime":"2019-02-11T10:00:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-11T16:40:36.000Z","uid":141151,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"ba49357e4877c34bd6106f8d5c3c3299d7443bb3","tid":1017239,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T10:00:42.000Z","msg":"美國民主黨迎來第九位總統候選人角逐者<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://big5.ftchinese.com/story/001081388?full=y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbig5.ftchinese.com%2Fstory%2F001081388%3Ffull%3Dy&d=hKO5vKCyTOC8%2FV9T1xBu13d5d2ehbLCfOFFYxDFDkZk%3D&h=57be4524\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://big5.ftchinese.com/story/001081388?full=y</a><br />\n<br />\n溫和派明尼蘇達州參議員埃米&bull;克羅布徹(Amy Klobuchar)周日成為第九位角逐總統候選人的民主黨人。該黨看來將引來史上角逐者最多的大選初選階段。<br />\n<br />\n來自中西部的這位政界人士加入角逐的前一天，進步派的馬薩諸塞州參議員、69歲的伊麗莎白&bull;沃倫(Elizabeth Warren)正式發起問鼎白宮的努力。這突顯出民主黨進步派與中間派之間的角力，這場角力將成為民主黨在2020年大選競選期間的主要斷層線之一。<br />\n<br />\n「這是我們一生中最至關重要的鬥爭。打造一個夢想有可能成真的美國、適合每個人生存發展的美國的鬥爭，」沃倫在發起她的競選時表示。<br />\n<br />\n這兩位參議員加入民主黨總統候選人的角逐之際，創紀錄數量的<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">女性</span></span>正力求打破白宮的「玻璃天花板」。加州參議員卡瑪拉&bull;哈里斯（Kamala Harris，中文名賀錦麗）和夏威夷眾議員圖爾西&bull;加巴德(Tulsi Gabbard)已發起競選努力，紐約州參議員柯爾斯滕&bull;吉利布蘭德(Kirsten Gillibrand)預計將效仿。<br />\n<br />\n現年58歲、<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">工人階級背景</span></span>的克羅布徹已擔任三任參議員，她被視為比沃倫更接近中間立場，但她也已將幫助消費者的議題（例如降低藥品價格）列為優先事項。<br />\n<br />\n民主黨總統候選人角逐者行列的規模和多樣性&mdash;&mdash;其中包括兩名<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">非裔美國人參議員、西裔角逐者</span></span>朱利安&bull;卡斯特羅(Julian Castro)以及<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">公開的同性戀者</span></span>皮特&bull;布蒂吉格(Pete Buttigieg)&mdash;&mdash;表明，該黨圍繞擊敗特朗普這個目標的勢頭很足。但這種情況也揭示出，該黨在哪一種候選人可以擊敗他的問題上缺乏共識。"},{"pid":"d981633dc21d1eaf17c5cc7d76d204f795128598","tid":1017239,"uid":40478,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T10:03:22.000Z","msg":"一盤散沙"},{"pid":"9d45b27cc4979a1cf2f04dfa40ef34ca6ca97712","tid":1017239,"uid":58670,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"d981633dc21d1eaf17c5cc7d76d204f795128598","tid":1017239,"uid":40478,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T10:03:22.000Z","msg":"一盤散沙"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T10:10:31.000Z","msg":"GOP 2016年有十七個，當中有十二個有參加初選。其實多人選係正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7389c601465a11740937b6e3ff9d01481d6cbc67","tid":1017239,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T10:11:29.000Z","msg":"總之你唔選佢就係種族主義 白人至上啦"},{"pid":"cc726d25904cbc8741e794ff31384d3acd66525c","tid":1017239,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T10:14:58.000Z","msg":"今時今日係咪正常人參選輸硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71956150cc4c341b4ff00f2532726b8fbf596b32","tid":1017239,"uid":53811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T10:20:29.000Z","msg":"佢地全部要素合體做一個可能有少少勝算"},{"pid":"726b3e5770f19350de82dcb1b1a7a78af41aeea4","tid":1017239,"uid":40979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T10:26:03.000Z","msg":"要說服The Rock幫佢選先有得玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a718482ad2053aa039d78517cf2542259eb3f1be","tid":1017239,"uid":141151,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"71956150cc4c341b4ff00f2532726b8fbf596b32","tid":1017239,"uid":53811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T10:20:29.000Z","msg":"佢地全部要素合體做一個可能有少少勝算"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T10:31:28.000Z","msg":"少數族裔女性同性戀伊斯蘭教徒素食環保重稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/slick.gif\" class=